snippet.title: Swimsanity! - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Swimsanity! is now available on Nintendo Switch! Dive into this multiplayer underwater shooter with action-packed Co-op and Versus game modes!

Available Now: https://nintendo.com/games/detail/swimsanity-switch/
